### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → PLANS (Escalated) — /api/v1/admin/plans
### ============================================================================

### Get escalated plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/escalated?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Approve escalated plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/{{planId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Reject escalated plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/{{planId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Plan does not meet clinical guidelines"
}

### Preview escalated plan PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/{{planId}}/preview-pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Preview escalated plan summary PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/{{planId}}/preview-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
